3)  Download Linux Kernel: git clone https://github.com/raspberrypi/linux.git
    Install cross compiler: sudo apt-get install gcc-arm-linux-gnueabihf
                            sudo apt-get install gcc-aarch64-linux-gnu
                            
    Execute:    KERNEL=kernel7
                make ARCH=arm CROSS_COMPILE=arm-linux-gnueabihf- bcm2709_defconfig
                
                make ARCH=arm CROSS_COMPILE=arm-linux-gnueabihf- menuconfig
                press exit
                
                (with time measurement)
                time make ARCH=arm CROSS_COMPILE=arm-linux-gnueabihf- -j4 zImage modules
                took:   real    26m45,496s
                        user    62m0,869s
